# gstack Battle Rules

1. Read `GSTACK_BATTLE_WORKFLOW.md` and `CUSTOM_FRAMEWORK.md`.
2. BA before design: `docs/BA_BRIEF.md` from `01b-ba-analysis.md`.
3. Designer before code: `DESIGN.md` + plan-design-review ≥8/10; responsive section required.
4. Designer may use WebSearch and `/browse` for visual research (3–5 min).
5. Eng before scaffold: plan-eng-review locks API + SQLite.
6. Docs required: core (BA_BRIEF, PRD, api-spec, …) + governance (WORKFLOW_MANIFEST, TRACEABILITY, …).
7. DEMO_ACCOUNTS.md + seed when BA_BRIEF requires login.
8. api-spec.md must use concrete paths — run `verify-docs.sh` after QA.
9. Full-stack mandatory: client + Express + SQLite — no mock-only.
10. Web responsive mandatory: test 375px before Flutter gate.
11. QA must produce `docs/QA_REPORT.md`.
12. Handoff: `03e-handoff-scorecard.md` → HANDOFF + WORKFLOW_SCORECARD + FRAMEWORK_EVIDENCE/.
13. Flutter gate after web QA: AskUserQuestion YES/NO.
14. PPTX: 3 parts — product / gstack / custom gstack.
15. Tick FRAMEWORK_CHECKLIST.md per step.
